 rage alessandro plung the knife maria breast fourteen time final came to sens thought maria dead frantic threw the knife behind closet lock room the cri babi teresa on land brought the attent to assunta father alessandro as babi unattend danger fall off ran hous find maria who cover blood drag door when ask happen said alessandro stab her he want make wrong would not the ambul arriv polic took alessandro away as the ambul carri maria hospit larg crowd follow foot the doctor hospit held hope for poor littl maria the fr jerom gave maria first communion came administ last rite give holi viaticum he ask maria would forgiv murder ye for the love jesu forgiv him wish one day join me in paradis may god forgiv him alread have maria die three clock alessandro tri found guilti maria death but age sentenc thirti year in prison after eight year violent prison show ing regret crime saw dream midst of field flower maria hold bunch white lili to him soon later wrote local bishop beg god par grave sin commit he later gave testimoni in maria beatif less three year later ju ne th maria canonis assunta goretti the first mother ever present daughter canonis may st maria goretti help us to be pure grant us the strength die rather commit mortal sin saint maria goretti pray us brendan arthur internet simon giaeb cc monash edu au viva cristo rey long live christ king